---
title: Swingball Meatballs with Smoked Tomato Linguine
description: When we were kids a skipping rope and a hula hoop constituted a pretty good evening’s entertainment*. As the years went by a swingball set appeared in the garden and then it wasn’t long before our humble Frisbee became a long range Aerobie. Whatever your summertime pleasure, we put this little number together with speed and ease in mind, so you’ve got more time for the fun stuff.
*OK, maybe we’re not that old. Though Head Chef Patrick might be. Shhhhhhhh.
